Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:06.53,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Pokud nevyhrajeme, jsme mrtví!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:07.52,CRKuro,KIYOSHI,0,0,0,,Cože?
